CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper May 9, 1953, pg. 34, reads: "At Kingsley House 'Come And See Night' - When Kingsley House held its 'Come and See Night' at the East End Community Center Tuesday night, one of the dance numbers performed by the young girls was based on a tight-rope act... In the bottom photo, members of the photography section of the Newspaper Club at the center as they snapped two of the dancers. Wayne Beasley and Adrian Page during another number. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Boys from newspaper club taking photographs of dancers Wayne Beasley and Adrian Page at Kingsley House "Come and See Night" program at East End Community Center
